   SG_ PumpCurrent : 31|16@0+ (0.001,0) [0|65.535] "mA" ECU
   SG_ VirtualGroundFault : 41|2@0+ (1,0) [0|3] "" ECU
   SG_ NernstCellFault : 43|2@0+ (1,0) [0|3] "" ECU
   SG_ PumpCurrentFault : 45|2@0+ (1,0) [0|3] "" ECU
   SG_ HeaterFault : 47|2@0+ (1,0) [0|3] "" ECU
   SG_ Status : 55|8@0+ (1,0) [0|255] "" ECU
   SG_ HeaterDuty : 63|8@0+ (1,0) [0|100] "%" ECU

