   SG_ Egt1 : 7|12@0+ (1,-50) [0|4095] "degC" ECU
   SG_ Egt2 : 11|12@0+ (1,-50) [0|4095] "degC" ECU
   SG_ Egt3 : 31|12@0+ (1,-50) [0|4095] "degC" ECU
